# Window Actions
Maximize* Mod4 m;
MaximizeVertical* Mod4 Ctrl m;
MaximizeHorizontal* Mod4 Shift m;
Shade* Mod4 s;
Stick* Mod4 t;
AlwaysOnTop* Mod4 o;
AlwaysBelow* Mod4 l;
Iconify* Mod4 i;
Close* Mod4 c;

# Movement
NudgeHorizontal* Mod4 b : -10;
NudgeHorizontal* Mod4 f : 10;
NudgeVertical* Mod4 p : -10;
NudgeVertical* Mod4 n : 10;

NextFrame* Alt Tab;

# Groups
NextInFrame* Ctrl Alt Right;
PrevInFrame* Ctrl Alt Left;

# Desktops
NextWorkspace* Alt Right;
PrevWorkspace* Alt Left;

GoToWorkspace* Alt F1 : 1;
GoToWorkspace* Alt F2 : 2;
GoToWorkspace* Alt F3 : 3;
GoToWorkspace* Alt F4 : 4;
GoToWorkspace* Alt F5 : 5;
GoToWorkspace* Alt F6 : 6;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F1 : 1;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F2 : 2;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F3 : 3;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F4 : 4;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F5 : 5;
SendToWorkspace* Mod4 F6 : 6;

# External commands
Exec* Mod4 x : xterm ;


# This requires you to have your xkb set up properly
# (These are the 'extra buttons' used on many keyboards)
Exec* None XF86AudioPrev : xmms -r;
Exec* None XF86AudioNext : xmms -f;
Exec* None XF86AudioPlay : xmms -t;
Exec* None XF86AudioStop : xmms -s;


# Wm actions
Reload* Ctrl Alt Shift Delete;
Restart* Ctrl Alt Delete;
RestartOther* Ctrl Alt g : gnome-session;
Exit* Ctrl Alt End;
